2. A contact working group, comprising representatives of key ministries and departments, development institutions and expert organizations, was set up for public discussion and agreeing with all stakeholders the adoption and implementation of energy efficiency standards, as well as other technical issues (labeling, normative documents, regulations) related to the project activities; 
